---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="IT & SaaS Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">

<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-400">IT & SaaS Cybersecurity Solutions</h1>

<p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Protect cloud infrastructure, APIs, and digital platforms with CI/CD aware security and runtime protection.</p>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8 text-center">Key Security Requirements for IT & SaaS</h2>
<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Cloud Security & CSPM</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Continuous posture management and misconfiguration detection for cloud workloads.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Tenable</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">API Protection</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Secure APIs against abuse and data exposure.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Trellix / Forcepoint</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Identity & Access Management</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Centralized identity and least-privilege controls for SaaS platforms.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: ARCON</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Vulnerability Management</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Find and fix vulnerabilities in code, containers, and infrastructure.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Tenable</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</main>

</Layout>
